{"tid":1342763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議每區成立民間自衞隊","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:02.000Z","uid":277441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65273d16e5b34dce13bdc4d7150ca34ac6e59947","tid":1342763,"uid":277441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"每一區都成立自衞隊，要通過審查方式入隊<br />\n每個區既自衞隊成員出少少錢，自己租一個地方作為自己區既總部，另外每區都要有一個代表，咁樣的話我地每次行動都會順暢好多。<br />\n我地唔可以再只係連登討論，我地要有部署<br />\n唔可以每次都靠即時決定，好似今日元朗咁<br />\n無辜市民受傷，立場記者，rock哥受傷，<br />\n正義議員受傷，警黑勾結，我地只可以自救<br />\n既然正義遲遲未到<br />\n就等我地每一個人成為正義"},{"pid":"9c42b523476b80ff93de03aa7055de79f3358351","tid":1342763,"uid":258409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a25027b7aa1c2f8df648015fad6a377dc4ab20","tid":1342763,"uid":277441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c42b523476b80ff93de03aa7055de79f3358351","tid":1342763,"uid":258409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}